  ('dive-liveaboard-hurricane', 'caribbean', '11C', '{"liveaboard","ocean"}', '{"activities"}', 'lookahead', 'lookahead', 'Dive liveaboards — the pros watch the weather for you', 'Liveaboard trips are planned far ahead on tight weather windows — which works in your favor: operators watch the tropics professionally and reroute or reschedule around weather as routine. Book outside the Aug–Oct peak where you can, protect the trip when you reserve, and let the captain and the forecast do the worrying.', null, null, null, null, 'favor outside Aug–Oct peak', 'curated', 70, null, null)
